OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA mainly dry and bright day,
OL,6,Fperhaps the odd light shower. Turning
OL,7,Fcloudier through the afternoon with
OL,8,Fsome patchy rain arriving later,
OL,9,Fpossibly heavy towards the evening.
OL,10,FFreshening afternoon winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA cloudy, damp evening with
OL,13,Foutbreaks of rain. Turning mainly dry
OL,14,Ffor the rest of the night with some
OL,15,Fclearer spells developing. Risk of
OL,16,Fstrong winds on northern coasts later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
