OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FA bright and largely dry
OL,6,Fday, with plenty of sunny spells and
OL,7,Fjust the slight chance of an isolated
OL,8,Flight shower. Breezy with occasional
OL,9,Fstrong winds on northern coasts.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FA
OL,12,Fchangeable period but often dry and
OL,13,Fbright with sunny spells. Some patchy
OL,14,Frain or a few showers possible at
OL,15,Ftimes, mainly in the west.
